This allows you, by mixing those colors to create pastel shades, this expands the color selection enormously.

column5: The HitLights Easy-Plug Kit is designed to offer you an easy way to establish ambiance with our Warm White LED light strips. This kit incorporates flexible, indoor strips with an IP rating of IP-30. This means that they can be used for applications or areas where the strips will not be in contact with moisture, and offer a perfect solution for many indoor projects including cabinet lights, stair lighting, media lighting, living areas, etc. Our strips can be cut after every 3rd LED, and have 3M adhesive backing. S be cut to custom lengths, and mounting the entire light spool is extremely easy! This 12-volt,  LED light is safe to touch. The strip does not emit any UV or infrared light, and lasts up to 50,000 hours. The HitLights Warm White Easy-Plug Kit is simple to install, and adds a highlight effect to nearly any area in the home! The strip runs on only 1.5 Watts per foot, which is great for the environment and your electric bill! It also has a lifespan of over 50,000 hours, equating to over 10 years of using the lights 8 hours/day! This Easy-Plug kit also includes a dial dimmer and a 24 watt power adapter, so you have everything required to simply plug and play! The dial dimmer can bring the brightness to any level to suit your project’s special needs!
